title: Reverse Phone Detective Lookup [Lookup Phone Numbers]
description:
About (from developer):

Reverse Phone Detective Lookup contains a database of hundreds of millions of cell and unlisted phone numbers, complete with information about the owner. The phone numbers and information about each owner is collected from public information, data brokers, and other confidential sources. This program allows you to search the database and get free limited access. There is a small fee if you want the unlimited version.

This program goes for $39.95
